sentences: Little Green Cars were an Irish indie rock band formed in Dublin in 2008.
The band announced on 21 March 2019 that they were disbanding.
Little Green Cars were formed in Dublin in 2008.
The band has played at the 2013 SXSW music festival in Austin, Texas, the Coachella Music Festival in California, Lollapalooza 2013 in Chicago and the 2013 Osheaga festival in Montréal.
